  /**
   * Fetch many placeholders by document ID in one or few round trips.
   * Replaces N+1 loops of {@code findById}. Chunks the input at DEFAULT_IN_CHUNK_SIZE.
   * See JAVA_CODE_QUALITY.md §5.5.
